ss="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-1916_"><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-1917_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">As the autumn leaves start to fall and the air crisps up, there's something else in the air besides the scent of pumpkin spice – a sense of determination. It's October, and across the United Kingdom, individuals are gearing up for a transformative month, one that promises not just change, but a healthier, smoke-free future. Welcome to Stoptober, a nationwide initiative that's more than just a campaign – it's a movement towards better health and well-being.</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1919_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-1920_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kHOZwM hRBLBR pf-1921_">Definitions</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/flat-lay-with-bunch-of-cigarettes-isolated-on-grey-2023-11-27-05-29-49-utc.jpg?v=1709052050" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/flat-lay-with-bunch-of-cigarettes-isolated-on-grey-2023-11-27-05-29-49-utc.jpg?v=1709052050 1536w" width="1000" height="667" alt="Unlock Expert Quitting Strategies with ComplyPlus LMS This Stoptober - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Unlock Expert Quitting Strategies with ComplyPlus LMS This Stoptober - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fbyfCU cCdixN pf-1923_"/><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-1924_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by LightFieldStudios via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-1926_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Stoptober, an amalgamation of "stop" and "October", is an annual campaign spearheaded by Public Health England. It encourages smokers to quit smoking for the entire month of October, with the aim of promoting smoking cessation and raising awareness about the health benefits of quitting.
</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1928_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-1929_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kHOZwM hRBLBR pf-1930_">Key facts and statistics</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/3_3d527365-e6e0-4ae8-8fef-e7dbba0f7ff3.png?v=1709045105" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/3_3d527365-e6e0-4ae8-8fef-e7dbba0f7ff3.png?v=1709045105 1536w" width="1419" height="946" alt="Transform Your Health: A Guide to Our Smoking Cessation Courses - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Transform Your Health: A Guide to Our Smoking Cessation Courses - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fbyfCU cCdixN pf-1932_"/><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-1933_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by mohdizzuanbinroslan via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-1935_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Before we delve deeper into the significance of Stoptober, let's take a moment to understand the gravity of smoking and its impact on health:</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-kYHfwS lkFAWj pf-1937_"><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah cpQDEO pf-1938_">Smoking is the leading cause of preventable death worldwide, responsible for over 8 million deaths annually.</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah cpQDEO pf-1940_">In the UK alone, smoking-related diseases claim the lives of around 78,000 people each year.</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah cpQDEO pf-1942_">Despite the known health risks, approximately 14% of adults in the UK still smoke, highlighting the ongoing challenge of tobacco addiction.</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1944_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-1945_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kHOZwM hRBLBR pf-1946_">The Stoptober journey</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/pack-of-cigarettes-in-hand-isolated-on-white-back-2023-11-27-05-35-37-utc.jpg?v=1709052279" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/pack-of-cigarettes-in-hand-isolated-on-white-back-2023-11-27-05-35-37-utc.jpg?v=1709052279 1536w" width="1000" height="667" alt="Join the Success: How Our ComplyPlus LMS Supports Your Smoke-Free Journey - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Join the Success: How Our ComplyPlus LMS Supports Your Smoke-Free Journey - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fbyfCU cCdixN pf-1948_"/><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-1949_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by Angelov1 via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-1951_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><b>Committing to change</b> - Embarking on the Stoptober journey is more than just a personal decision – it's a commitment to better health and well-being. Throughout the month of October, participants are provided with a wealth of resources and support to aid them on their quit journey. From mobile apps to motivational emails and community support groups, Stoptober equips individuals with the tools they need to succeed.</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1953_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-typ